CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1955, pg. 26 reads: " Thousands Thrilled at Courier Home Service Fair...8. The Anheuser-Busch Company, makers of famous Budweiser Beer, had Eastern representative Wilbur Vaulx, assisted by Miss Sherlynn Dudley, in their booth...Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Wilbur Vaulx and Sherlynn Dudley standing in Budweiser booth in Syria Mosque for the 1955 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
